::DarkMouse::

She watched on the interoir base monitors that Sterotron was entering 
the base.  She activated the autoguns near the entrance and fire them 
on Stegotron.
"Paralysis, keep an eye on the other bots on those monitors.  It they 
get through, Black Aracnia would have us for lunch."  She kept aiming 
at Stegotron with the inside guns and aimed the autoguns at the other 
Maximals.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, TrikeJacob@n... wrote:
> As Stegotron is running toward the entrense, he is hit by one of 
the autoguns in the torso. He stumbles but manages to keep his 
footing and passes through the entrense of the base.
